            "id": "https://gaoxiaoxin.github.io/2022/07/12/%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95/ssh%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%B0GitHub/",
            "url": "https://gaoxiaoxin.github.io/2022/07/12/%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95/ssh%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%B0GitHub/",
            "title": "ssh连接不到Github",
            "date_published": "2022-07-12T03:27:33.914Z",
            "content_html": "<h3 id=\"起因\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#起因\">#</a> 起因</h3>\n<p>由于我来亲戚家旅游，所以就更换了 WiFi，但是┭┮﹏┭┮,Bug 它就出现了。当我想提交 GitHub 代码的时候，它就出现一个如下的 bug。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><figcaption><span>bug</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ssh: Could not resolve hostname github.com: No address associated with hostname</span><br><span class=\"line\">Please make sure you have the correct access rights</span><br><span class=\"line\">and the repository exists.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>它显示不能解析我的主机名 <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cDovL2dpdGh1Yi5jb20=\">github.com</span>, 没有与主机名关联的地址。<br>\n然后经过 Google 的话，它显示<br>\n<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3FxXzM0NzY5MTYyL2FydGljbGUvZGV0YWlscy8xMTczOTI1Njg=\"> https://blog.csdn.net/qq_34769162/article/details/117392568</span><br>\n 经过测试不出所料，我的网果然连不到 GitHub, 毫无反应。<br>\n<img data-src=\"https://tva4.sinaimg.cn/large/006xVoHRly8h44dzvyhwyj30ov02bgm9.jpg\" alt=\"\"><br>\n<img data-src=\"https://tva3.sinaimg.cn/large/006xVoHRly8h44e3n2gtyj30gn049gm2.jpg\" alt=\"\"><br>\n那就一个个试一下，首先去尝试 dns.（其实直接排除了代理）<br>\n那么正好了解一下 DNS。</p>\n<h4 id=\"什么是dns\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#什么是dns\">#</a> 什么是 DNS</h4>\n<h4 id=\"尝试解决\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#尝试解决\">#</a> 尝试解决</h4>\n<p>最终解决方案，重新本地生成了密钥，并且将这个密钥上传到了 GitHub。<br>\n<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"\">https://blog.csdn.net/zhouzhiwengang/article/details/124960506?spm=1001.2101.3001.6650.1&amp;utm_medium=distribute.pc_relevant.none-task-blog-2~default~CTRLIST~default-1-124960506-blog-117392568.pc_relevant_multi_platform_whitelistv1&amp;depth_1-utm_source=distribute.pc_relevant.none-task-blog-2~default~CTRLIST~default-1-124960506-blog-117392568.pc_relevant_multi_platform_whitelistv1&amp;utm_relevant_index=2</span><br>\n 可以看这个大哥的。</p>\n<div class=\"note warning\">\n<p>在重新生成前，建议把.ssh 文件夹 (不知道在哪来的可以去百度) 中的文件进行删除。然后再重新生成。</p>\n</div>\n",
            "tags": []
        }
    ]
}